videos.description: Jacques Patrick bounces to the outside and runs for 30 yards to put the Noles in Miami territory.
videos.headline: Patrick rips off big run for Florida State

videos.description: Miami's Kendrick Norton sacks James Blackman for a loss of six yards and then uses the quarterback's leg as a guitar after the play.
videos.headline: Norton plays the air guitar in sack celebration

videos.description: James Blackman's pass is intercepted by Michael Jackson who dives to make the catch to give Miami the ball with a minute to go in the first half.
videos.headline: Miami defense intercepts Blackman

videos.description: FSU head coach Jimbo Fisher says his offense needs to execute better inside the 40-yard line but he likes what he sees from his defense.
videos.headline: Fisher: Offense needs to be better in 2nd half

videos.description: Malik Rosier finds Ahmmon Richards down the field and completes a 32-yard pass to keep the Canes drive alive.
videos.headline: Miami gets big play to convert on 3rd down

videos.description: James Blackman's pass is intercepted by Dee Delaney and returned for 2 yards to give Miami the ball in FSU territory.
videos.headline: Blackman throws 2nd pick of the game

videos.description: Miami's Malik Rosier throws to the end zone and his pass is picked off by Stanford Samuels III resulting in a touchback.
videos.headline: FSU defense answers with an interception

videos.description: Malik Rosier drops back and then connects with Braxton Berrios who makes a back shoulder catch in the end zone giving the Canes the lead.
videos.headline: Miami scores on 21-yard catch by Berrios

videos.description: James Blackman zips it to Ryan Izzo for the 15-yard touchdown to tie the game.
videos.headline: Florida State ties game with TD from Blackman

videos.description: Braxton Berrios makes another impressive touchdown catch in the back of the end zone to  put Miami up with 5 minutes left to play.
videos.headline: Berrios strikes again with TD catch for the lead

videos.description: James Blackman drops back and throws a perfect 20-yard pass to Auden Tate who was open in the end zone to give the Noles the lead with 1:24 to play.
videos.headline: Florida State takes lead on big TD from Blackman

videos.description: Malik Rosier connects with Darrell Langham who dives into the end zone for the touchdown. The play was reviewed and upheld.
videos.headline: Miami scores game winning TD with six seconds left

videos.description: Miami head coach Mark Richt says he is proud of his quarterback and offense for stepping up when they needed it the most in Miami's 24-20 win over FSU.
videos.headline: Richt: 'It just matters that we won'

videos.description: In a back-and-forth battle in the fourth quarter, Darrell Langham scores the go-ahead touchdown with six seconds remaining to give the No. 13 Hurricanes a 24-20 win.
videos.headline: Miami tops Florida State in final seconds
